1.删除8008从节点
/app/redis-cluster/bin/redis-cli -a K6CJDjjnE9d0OxRjYNKZ --cluster del-node 192.168.0.61:8008 e1ec98aa87327564e4e9bf71edbde0fae0aace7c

2.删除8007主节点
/app/redis-cluster/bin/redis-cli -a K6CJDjjnE9d0OxRjYNKZ --cluster reshard 10.204.51.64:8007

